The President is pleased with the Supreme Court's decision in Whole Woman's Health v. Hellerstedt, as it protects women's rights and health. The Court ruled that restrictions on abortion clinics harm women's health and violate their constitutional rights. The President reaffirms his commitment to protecting women's access to safe and affordable healthcare and their right to make their own reproductive choices. He believes that when everyone has accessible and affordable healthcare, women's opportunities expand and the nation becomes stronger.